                    <description>&lt;p&gt;    Fix for unquoted string comparison:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;      error: bare words are no longer supported, please use &quot;...&quot;:&lt;br/&gt;
      redhat==&quot;redhat&quot; || redhat==&quot;fedora&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

